#Date: 11-01-2024
##Status: Accepted

##Context:
To design a user-friendly Visa Processing System, it is crucial to identify and understand the various personas involved and create user scenarios that encompass different use cases.

##Decision:
We will create detailed personas and user scenarios, focusing on usability aspects such as user interactions, needs, and pain points. This documentation will guide the design and development process to ensure a system that meets the diverse needs of users.

##Consequences:
The development team will have a clear understanding of user expectations, resulting in a system that is not only functional but also user-friendly and aligned with the needs of the target audience.
